Mozilla nisamäj kik'in achib'ila' richin nitikirisäx ajchijun kuchuq'a' kab'lajtäq taq t'ij chi winäq k'o ketamab'al richin nikito' ri koch'ojkib'al ruwinaq ajk'amaya'l.


;Products and Technology
Tikojil chuqa' na'ob'äl


;Mozilla Corporation, a wholly owned subsidiary of the Foundation, makes consumer Internet products that advance the same values outlined in the Mozilla Manifesto.
Mozilla Moloj, jun achpwäq chi chijun richinem ri Moloj, yerub'än taq rutikojil K'amaya'l kichin wi okisanela' nikoqaj ri taq ejqalem echolon pa ri Mozilla Manifiesto.


;Firefox, our flagship product, gives increased choice, privacy and security to 100s of millions of people around the world. Product exploration initiatives like our ‘connected devices’ program aim to bring more mainstream products with Mozilla values into the world. Technology initiatives like Rust and Mozilla’s online game centre aim to spread new thinking about open technology across the whole of the Internet industry.
Firefox, ri nïm qatikojil, nuya' jun nïm cha'oj, ichinanem chuqa' jikomal chi ke ri wok'altäq chi t'ij winaqi' chijun ruwach'ulew. Ri tikirisanïk samaj richin kikanoxik taq tikojil achi'el ri qanuk'samaj richin ‘okisan taq okisaxel’ kojqan chi nikajo' nikik'äm pe ch'aqa' chik taq tikojil kojqan kejqalem Mozilla pa ruwach'ulew. Tikirisanïk na'ob'äl samaj achi'el ri Rust chuqa' ri etz'anem jay pa k'amab'ey richim Mozilla nikajo' yekitaluj k'ak'a' taq na'oj chi rij jaqäl na'ob'äl pa ronojel ri ajb'anonem k'amaya'l.


;Mozilla Community
Rutinamit Mozilla


;The real power behind Mozilla is a global community of 10,000s of volunteers, allies and partners. Members of the Mozilla community participate by doing everything from contributing code to Firefox and <a href="%(url_learning)s">teaching digital literacy</a> to translating our software, organizing advocacy campaigns and writing the world's most referenced <a href="%(url_mdn)s">web developer site</a>.
Ri qitzij uchuqa' chi rij Mozilla ja ri chijun tinamït kichin 10.000 to'onela', achib'ila' chuqa' qawinaq. Ri taq ruwinaq rutinamit Mozilla yeto'on rik'in rub'anik ronojel, rik'in ri ruto'ik b'itz'ib' chi re Firefox chuqa' <a href="%(url_learning)s">retamaxik ajilal etamanem</a> chi re rutzalq'omanïk ri qakema', kinuk'ik taq rutzijol talunem chuqa' kitz'ib'axik ri taq <a href="%(url_mdn)s">ruxaq ajk'amaya'l kichin b'anonela'</a>.


